00:02:33.480 --> 00:02:35.240 align:middle line:84%
if there is some
mystery associated

00:02:35.240 --> 00:02:39.710 align:middle line:84%
with, say, some giant pyramid
or wall or statues someplace,

00:02:39.710 --> 00:02:43.340 align:middle line:84%
this is something that you can
actually go and investigate

00:02:43.340 --> 00:02:44.840 align:middle line:90%
yourself.

00:02:44.840 --> 00:02:45.830 align:middle line:90%
And that intrigued me.

00:02:45.830 --> 00:02:49.580 align:middle line:84%
I already liked to
travel and go to places

00:02:49.580 --> 00:02:54.270 align:middle line:84%
and was relatively well-versed
in many of these sites,

00:02:54.270 --> 00:02:55.970 align:middle line:90%
although there are so many.

00:02:55.970 --> 00:02:58.880 align:middle line:84%
I'm still learning about all
kinds of interesting sites

00:02:58.880 --> 00:03:00.170 align:middle line:90%
around the world.

00:03:00.170 --> 00:03:04.140 align:middle line:84%
I think of myself as a
scientifically-minded person.

