world starting in the mid '70s.

00:03:24.470 --> 00:03:27.830 align:middle line:10%
I returned to the
United States, and I

00:03:27.830 --> 00:03:30.410 align:middle line:10%
wanted to write some
books and keep traveling.

00:03:30.410 --> 00:03:33.290 align:middle line:84%
But at that point I wrote a book
called "The Hitchhiker's Guide

00:03:33.290 --> 00:03:34.970 align:middle line:90%
to Africa and Arabia."

00:03:34.970 --> 00:03:39.740 align:middle line:84%
This was mid-1980s, and this
was just as Apple computers were

00:03:39.740 --> 00:03:42.140 align:middle line:84%
