the first laser printers

00:03:42.140 --> 00:03:43.380 align:middle line:90%
and things like that.

00:03:43.380 --> 00:03:46.670 align:middle line:84%
And it was the beginning
of desktop publishing.

00:03:46.670 --> 00:03:49.700 align:middle line:10%
And at that point, I started
my own publishing company,

00:03:49.700 --> 00:03:53.900 align:middle line:10%
Adventures Unlimited Press,
realizing that this was a time

00:03:53.900 --> 00:03:57.106 align:middle line:10%
to be my own publisher.

00:03:57.106 --> 00:03:58.730 align:middle line:10%
And it was a difficult
time, but then I

00:03:58.730 --> 00:04:02.960 align:middle line:10%
